data.description:
Welcome to this 1800 sq. ft.  3bed /2bath home sitting on 2.1 beautiful acres. 
As you walk into the entry foyer you will see the living room that flows nicely into the cozy family room with a gas burning fireplace(2019). Then enter into a good size eat-in kitchen with stainless steel appliances and center island. The divided bedroom floor plan is a plus. The master bedroom offers a walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom with double vanity, lovely tiled tub and separate shower. There is also 2 additional spacious bedrooms, office room, and another full bath. Stepping outback onto the newly repainted deck you can enjoy nature. The outbuilding can be used to suit your needs. Newer roof (2019). Patio. Check it out today!
